------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

âš ï¸ Common Array Mistakes

* Forgetting arrays are zero-indexed
* Using `sort()` incorrectly with numbers
* Mutating arrays unintentionally
* Not returning value in `map()`

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ’¡ Best Practices

* Use `map`, `filter`, `reduce`
* Avoid unnecessary loops
* Keep arrays immutable when possible
* Use meaningful variable names

